video.title: Sin senos sí hay paraíso
video.synopsis: Born into a small town controlled by the mafia, an irate young woman seeks revenge on the forces that tore apart and wrongfully imprisoned her family.

episodes.synopsis: Hilda Santana visits her child’s grave and receives some terrible news. When she gives birth to a girl, she calls her by her eldest daughter’s name.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Catalina breaks her family’s rules and crosses the line her mother spoke about so often. Martina has to convince Catalina to operate on her breasts.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Daniela and Diabla get their way and Catalina’s family and boyfriend are arrested. An emissary steals an important document from the Santanas.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Catalina’s punishments at the correctional facility push her to the limit. Daniela asks to have Nachito freed and they hire him as her bodyguard.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Catalina escapes from the hospital but her freedom is short-lived. Diabla knows that the marriage certificate gives Hilda right to Marcial's fortune.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Tired of being abused in the jail, Catalina is pushed to her limit and tries to defend herself. Dr. Rico loses his job for helping her.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Nachito signs the documents without knowing what they mean. Albeiro admits his guilt. A journalist investigates the case and accuses the mayor’s wife.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Diabla gets the Marín Santanas and Nachito out of jail before the journalists and authorities show up. Then, she hires a hacker.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: The guards make Catalina sign a document saying she wasn’t physically or psychologically abused. She vows she’ll get revenge on Diabla and her goons.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla and Colonel Herrera discuss the Cerón case. Catalina’s thirst for vengeance leads her to a bad decision.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Two options to make dirty money tempt Catalina. The journalist visits Catalina’s parents and they leave him on the street. His life is at risk.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Catalina confronts her parents, blames them for locking her up all those years and demands that they tell her the truth about her past.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Nachito begs Daniela not to kill him. Octavio must get the Santanas to sell him the house. They accuse the journalist of drug trafficking.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Nachito is threatened by Daniela and has to accept Diabla’s requests in order to protect his mother. Martina sells Catalina’s “services” to Octavio.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Nachito gives in to Diabla’s request in order to protect his mother. Jotica gets the Santanas’s house back. Hilda holds the key to her fortune.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Nachito will have to pass Diabla’s test to free himself from her punishments. Herrera rebels, and Diabla blackmails him.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Daniela’s obsession with Nachito makes her disobey her mother. Gato Gordo and Octavio compete for Catalina. Herrera interviews the mayor.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Catalina accepts Gato Gordo’s gift but lies to her parents. The mayor and his wife argue about Catalina’s threat. Diabla makes her power known.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro goes to the meeting thinking that it’s only with Jotica but there’s a surprise in store for him. Martina offers Catalina a juicy advance.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro goes to the meeting and finds Jotica with a catheter. Gato Gordo asks Diabla to use her route.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Diabla forces Nachito to kill Colonel Herrera. Marcial promises the Santanas that once he is free he’ll give them Catalina the elder’s money.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Pipe confesses that he was recruited like Nachito and promises to help him. Killing the colonel is Nachito’s acid test to save his mother.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Octavio sees specters and thinks that it’s Catalina the elder. Daniel, Cata and Lucía follow Daniela to see if she’ll lead them to Diabla and Nachito.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Catalina goes into Diabla’s ranch to find Nachito. Daniela asks her mother to free the love of her life. Aníbal finds out what his wife did.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Diabla must accept her daugther’s relationship with Nachito. Marcial wants to free Aurelio Jaramillo, imprisoned in the USA, to kill his worst enemy.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Catalina finds out the hard truth about her sister and father. Pelambre asks for forgiveness. Catalina will surrender to Gato Gordo on two conditions.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Catalina looks for Pelambre where her sister died. He still wants to kill Diabla but doesn’t have the power or men to do it.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Daniela undresses in front of Nachito. Diabla orders Franklin to torture Lucía. Martina takes a picture of Daniela with Nachito.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Martina gives Catalina one more day to finish Gato Gordo off. Daniel is worried that Lucía’s life is at stake. Marcial knows where she is.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: The time has come for Pelambre to avenge Catalina the elder. The mayor is furious with his wife. Diabla keeps Daniela locked up.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Pelambre is carried out of Diabla’s house on a stretcher. Daniela provokes Catalina and gives Nachito a new order.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Diabla thinks that Catalina the elder is still alive. The mayor says that the assassin survived six shots. Martina goes after Catalina.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Gato Gordo kidnaps Catalina to operate on her breasts. Marcial wants to off Diabla. Daniela visits her mother in the hospital and gets some advice.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Daniela keeps trying to make Nachito fall in love with her. Later, she goes crazy trying to find out where she is and who kidnapped her.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Diabla and Albeiro threaten each other about their daughters. Daniela and Marcial talk about the past. Catalina is shocked by her transformation.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Catalina is thirsting for revenge. Diabla tortures and pressures Pipe for letting them kidnap her daughter. Daniela finds out about her mother’s past.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Diabla gets furious and argues with Aníbal about the lawsuit. The mayor has good lawyers but she has a better idea. Daniela grows closer to Marcial.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Marcial celebrates Titi’s arrival and thanks him for his help. As a father, he spoils his daughter and hugs her for the first time.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Catalina plans to take revenge on Diabla. Albeiro and his wife would give up their inheritance to get their daughter back.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Diabla is obsessed with the idea that Catalina the elder is alive. In order to rescue her daughter, she agrees on a 48-hour period with the police.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Catalina takes advantage of the opportunity to ask her doctor to stop calling her parents. Marcial visits Pelambre and they have an emotional goodbye.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Catalina’s parents are desperate and Diabla threatens them. They pressure Catalina’s doctor to release her. Gato Gordo is losing his patience.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: Diabla and Octavio Rangel make a pact. She knows that the TEA agents are tailing her and panics. Daniel looks for Aurora, the journalist’s mother.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: The plastic surgeon has an idea for Catalina. Jota follows Vanessa and discovers her stark reality. Diabla presses Nachito to find out about Daniela.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Jota and Vanessa want to escape the brothel but they can’t do it alone. With Albeiro’s help they will try to outsmart a human trafficking network.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Gato Gordo plans a welcome party for the new Catalina even though she’s hurt by what they did to her. Catalina and the doctor have a heart to heart.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Before sleeping with him, Catalina asks Gato Gordo for twice the amount they had agreed upon. Meanwhile, Diabla's men prepare to attack the mansion.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: The attack on Gato Gordo’s mansion works in Catalina’s favor. A masked Nachito sees the love of his life and thinks that she slept with Gato Gordo.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Pipe can’t bear to see Nachito so excited about saving his mother and tells him the truth. Catalina tells her friends and Jota what happened.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and her friends follow the clues from Octavio’s letter. Daniela asks to say goodbye to her mother and warns her that they want to kill her.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Daniela makes a terrible decision to distract her father. Catalina and her friends follow the clues her older sister left about the money.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Marcial and his armed men attack Diabla’s mansion. Catalina and her friends don’t find the loot her sister left. Octavio sets up a date with Diabla.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Diabla concocts her next plan. Daniela escapes from the hospital and meets up with her mother. Titi takes the blame for not killing Diabla.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Catalina finds her sister’s money and puts her revenge scheme into action. Marcial and his men escape from the TEA and plan the attack on Diabla.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Diabla’s plan is a success. Daniela visits her in the hospital and becomes her accomplice. Diabla manages to fool everyone except Marcial.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: Anxious to take out her implants, Catalina visits the doctor but another operation is very dangerous. Diabla confronts Octavio.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: After finding his daughter Albeiro rejects her and will hear no explanations. Nachito admits to Pipe that he still loves Catalina.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: Diabla puts Aníbal to the test. Catalina hides 40,000 dollars in the house and divides the rest among her friends.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Right when Nachito is ready to get Catalina back, Mugroso changes the plans. Catalina is confused, did she lose him? Did Daniela steal him away?
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Someone unexpectedly interrupts the alleged funeral of Diabla. Daniela’s men obey and beat Albeiro. Catalina meets Titi at the cemetery.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Diabla orders her men to kill everyone who knows she’s alive or who stops her from going home. The TEA grants Marcial and Titi supervised probation.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: A call reveals an evil plan. Catalina confirms that Daniela is Diabla’s daughter. Mugroso and his accomplices stage the crime scene.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Catalina calls the neighborhood together to prevent another tragedy. Meanwhile, Albeiro recovers from his injuries. Daniela tries to seduce Nachito.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: Daniela leaves her bodyguards at home, which draws them closer to Diabla's fortune. One of Hilda’s ex-cellmates helps her flee and hide in a ranch.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Nachito wins Daniela over and convinces her to help him--she’ll be the perfect alibi. The Maríns start a new life. Mugroso continues his plans.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Diabla cries inconsolably over her mother’s death. Nachito wipes the fingerprints clean. Titi is on Catalina’s trail. Pipe has a proposal.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: Catalina’s house explodes. Catalina learns that Pipe left documents for Nachito. Albeiro goes crazy when he finds out his daughter has a cell phone.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: When Capitan Pérez is pressured by Diabla to find the Maríns’s remains, he creates false evidence. Pipe hides the stolen money.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Valentina visits Adriana in the hospital. Albeiro and Hilda have no idea about the explosion. Diabla wants to go to her mother’s funeral.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Valentina want to avenge Adriana’s death. Diabla sees the Maríns alive. Nachito warns Daniela about her stepfather’s evil intentions.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Valentina get the weapons and start training to carry out their plan. Vanessa mourns her daughter’s death. They bury Diabla’s mother.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: Catalina, Nachito and Valentina threaten Daniela with death but Marcial and Capitán Pérez step in to avoid a tragedy.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Valentina consider paying someone to kill Daniela, although this would mean spending all the money Catalina's sister left her family.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Nachito and Catalina dream about a future together. Aníbal accuses Nachito of a robbery. An ironic cackle turns into a clue.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: Diabla reappears before Aníbal’s eyes and threatens him. Nachito gives the Maríns valuable documents.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: Martina fools herself about Titi, who boasts he is the best narco, but his heart belongs to another woman. Nachito goes to the ranch with Catalina.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Adriana’s burial is the perfect time to attack. Diabla orders her men to eliminate Catalina and Hilda. Aníbal negotiates murder terms.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: One of Aníbal’s bodyguards becomes a murderer. A massacre is about to erupt. Adriana’s final goodbye has a huge turnout. Marcial is depressed.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: The Maríns and their allies meet to make a decision. Catalina, Nachito and Valentina show their weapons and desire to fight but not everyone agrees.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Diabla threatens to kill her doctor. Marcial might never walk again after his suicide attempt. Gato Gardo wants to take Martina’s life.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Gato Gordo takes control and puts the plan into action. Diabla puts a hefty sum on the heads of the Maríns and Pipe’s mother.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Nachito swear their eternal love. Capitan Pérez suffers the consequences of selling his soul to Diabla. Catalina’s father loses his mind.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: Nachito convinces Albeiro that Catalina is the love of his life. Titi goes to the hospital to visit Marcial, who is in the depths of depression.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: The Maríns, Jota, Vanessa and Valentina unite forces to open up Diabla’s grave. Daniela is taken over by jealousy and decides it’s time for revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: The Maríns and their allies take a DNA sample from one of Diabla’s victims and then make a key decision. Titi and Gato Gordo shake on a business deal.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: The plan is clear: it will have two phases. Aníbal is Diabla’s next victim. Martina is in love with a trafficker and her mother gives her some advice.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: Marcial gives the TEA agents the information they need to find and capture Diabla. This is the only way the first phase of the plan will work.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: Hilda and Albeiro give the TEA agents information about Diabla. Meanwhile, she sends her men to the ranch to finish off Catalina and her family.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: Hilda and Albeiro return to the ranch and Albeiro faces Diabla’s men. Catalina swears she won’t harm Diabla and Daniela in exchange for Nachito.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: Diabla and her daughter go to the ranch to look for the money and then slip away. However, fate has a surprise in store for them.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: Everyone thinks Catalina la Grande is dead but she is alive and well. She made a deal with the TEA and now has a new life in the United States.
episodes.title: Catalina, la sobreviviente

episodes.synopsis: Catalina, now Virginia Fernández, starts her life in the U.S. Albeiro professes his eternal love to her before her “grave.”
episodes.title: Nace Virginia Fernández

episodes.synopsis: Martín offers Virginia employment as an undercover TEA agent. Soraya tries to seduce Santiago with deceit.
episodes.title: Catalina se une a la TEA

episodes.synopsis: Virginia returns to Colombia to bury her past and give Jota instructions. Yésica goes to Mexico to make a deal. Virginia is given a promotion.
episodes.title: Virginia escribe su destino

episodes.synopsis: 20 years go by. Yésica is a powerful drug trafficker. When she finds out that la Diabla isn’t dead, Virginia goes to Colombia to confront her enemy.
episodes.title: 20 años después

episodes.synopsis: Virginia exposes la Diabla with a DNA test and escorts her to a prison in the U.S. The Maríns spend their first night in la Diabla’s mansion.
episodes.title: Dulce justicia

episodes.synopsis: Virginia is rewarded for capturing la Diabla but first, she, Marcial, Hilda, and Albeiro will all have to testify.
episodes.title: El que la hace, la paga

episodes.synopsis: El Titi suggests that he, Daniela, and Gato Gordo all work together as partners. Daniela agrees to run la Diabla’s routes if el Titi kills Catalina.
episodes.title: Entre suspicacias y trampas

episodes.synopsis: Martín wants Catalina to go to Colombia undercover and trap el Titi. Daniela and Aníbal offer to team up with el Titi and Gato Gordo.
episodes.title: La nueva misión de Virginia

episodes.synopsis: Hilda and Albeiro have to testify against la Diabla. Yésica plans her escape from prison. Virginia informs her children that they will go to Colombia.
episodes.title: El momento de la verdad

episodes.synopsis: Virginia offers Yésica a reduced penalty if she pleads guilty but she has two key witnesses who could bring her down.
episodes.title: Negocios entre enemigas

episodes.synopsis: Yésica records the conversation she has with the prison director. Daniela accuses Hernán Darío of stealing money from the safe.
episodes.title: Pasaporte a la libertad

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Pequeña submits to Daniela. Martín tells Virginia to seduce el Titi and trap him. La Diabla teams up with Mayra.
episodes.title: Estrategia amorosa

episodes.synopsis: Santiago asks Virginia to quit the TEA so that they both can spend more time with their children. Yésica blackmails the director and plans to escape.
episodes.title: Una chica mala

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Pequeña and Hernán Darío make love. Yésica meets her new lawyer. The prison director is forced to consent to la Diabla’s conditions.
episodes.title: La Diabla en control

episodes.synopsis: Yésica hasn't made a decision about Virginia's proposal. La Diabla threatens her. Marcial gets a feeling that Titi is going to kill him.
episodes.title: Castigo, amenazas y muerte

episodes.synopsis: Hilda and Albeiro find Catalina la Grande's grave empty. Yésica finds out the details for her escape and Titi tries to kill Marcial.
episodes.title: Tumba vacía y posible fuga

episodes.synopsis: Hilda and Albeiro are excited to get to Miami. Virginia is tormented after seeing her mother and her first love but Albeiro finds her.
episodes.title: Sentimientos encontrados

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla's escape plan takes shape in jail. Virginia is flustered after seeing her mother and Albeiro. Hilda demands to know what Albeiro is hiding.
episodes.title: Fuga en marcha

episodes.synopsis: Martín sets up a meeting between Virginia and Albeiro in an office at the courthouse. They intercept the van transporting la Diabla and three inmates.
episodes.title: Encuentro electrizante

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro tells Hilda that he was with Catalina la Grande and that she never died but Hilda doesn't believe him.
episodes.title: Sorpresa para Hilda

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro and Santiago meet. Chuky takes photos of Daniela and her step-father kissing and taking each other's clothes off. La Diabla worries everyone.
episodes.title: La Diabla, suelta

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro tells Catalina la Pequeña her mother is in a coma after making sure that she is alive. La Diabla makes it to Mexico for a meeting with Chalo.
episodes.title: Un secreto llega a su fin

episodes.synopsis: Santiago tells Catalina la Grande and Albeiro that Hilda will recover but when she wakes up, she'll have amnesia and have to start all over again.
episodes.title: Pérdida de memoria

episodes.synopsis: Hilda doesn't recognize Albeiro and attacks him with scissors. Yésica visits her sister in Venezuela. Titi orders his men to scare Catalina.
episodes.title: Hilda, fuera de sus cabales

episodes.synopsis: Hilda is released and everyone travels to Colombia. Titi's men go to the hospital to kill Catalina la Pequeña. Yésica steals her sister's passport.
episodes.title: De vuelta a Colombia

episodes.synopsis: Mariana hides some marijuana in Albeiro's belongings. Titi's hitmen kill a patient by accident and Catalina la Pequeña is still alive.
episodes.title: Blanco equivocado

episodes.synopsis: Marcial finds out that Titi was behind the hospital attack. Catalina and her family make it to Colombia. La Diabla becomes Amparo to cross the border.
episodes.title: Catalina en su terreno

episodes.synopsis: While Albeiro and Hernán Darío take Hilda to the hospital, Titi's hitmen take advantage of the opportunity to attack the house.
episodes.title: Las Catalinas se conocen

episodes.synopsis: Marcial and Catalina la Grande are reunited after 20 years and he apologizes to her. Catalina la Pequeña feels guilty for murdering two men.
episodes.title: Reencuentros y despedidas

episodes.synopsis: Marcial tells Titi that he's ready to die. Catalina la Grande and Santiago invite Albeiro and Hernán Darío to spend the night at their house.
episodes.title: El dolor de El Titi

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla makes it to Pereira. Everyone realizes that Marcial has died and that Titi is behind it. Catalina la Grande remembers her time with Marcial.
episodes.title: Recuerdos con Marcial

episodes.synopsis: Las Diablas reach the new ranch and plan to build an emergency tunnel. Hilda recovers part of her memory but she is referred to a psychiatrist.
episodes.title: Hilda a la defensiva

episodes.synopsis: Chuky burns the money that Daniela hid. The Captain is going to frame Chuky for Marcial's death. La Diabla stays on the street.
episodes.title: Las Diablas tocan fondo

episodes.synopsis: The police arrest Albeiro and Jota for burning down Las Diablas' house. Yésica is furious when Daniela admits that she slept with Titi.
episodes.title: Daniela se confiesa

episodes.synopsis: Mariana gets naked in front of Hernán Darío. Catalina la Grande sees them together and Mariana cuts her veins. Hilda is taken to the psychiatric ward.
episodes.title: Mariana sin límites

episodes.synopsis: Martín tells Virginia how to get to Titi and Gato Gordo: by moving to their old neighborhood. The agent traps Martina and wants her to be a TEA spy.
episodes.title: Estrategia de la TEA

episodes.synopsis: Hilda digs up the past and throws it in Virginia's face in front of Santiago. Mayra and Flavia join Las Diablas to set up a new cartel in Mexico City.
episodes.title: Las fichas de La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: Gato Gordo and Titi film their meeting with their partners. Daniela suggests that Titi kill Gato Gordo. Nacho is disappointed by Catalina la Pequeña.
episodes.title: Lección de madre

episodes.synopsis: Calvo and his men attack Gato Gordo's ranch but he manages to escape with Titi. Las Diablas and Flavia prepare Mayra to become the cocaine queen.
episodes.title: Traición de socios

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro and Jota get out of jail. Gato Gordo wants to make a claim about the attack on his ranch. Chuky organizes a vigil for Marcial.
episodes.title: Pensamientos fuera de lugar

episodes.synopsis: Titi suspects that Daniela gave the order to kill him so he confronts her but she denies it. Yésica changes her plan: she'll have to do it herself.
episodes.title: Cambio de planes

episodes.synopsis: Virginia starts acting as an undercover agent in front of Paola and Martina. Gato Gordo gets shot in a fight.
episodes.title: El pasado regresa

episodes.synopsis: Titi is excited to hear Catalina la Grande's voice and wants to see her. She shows up in the neighborhood and sees her old friends.
episodes.title: Se reavivan los sentimientos

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Pequeña hears her sister yelling at her daughter and finds out what happened with Hernán Darío. Titi dreams of being number one.
episodes.title: Mariana, un ser sin alma

episodes.synopsis: A heartbroken Catalina la Pequeña confronts Hernán Darío about his betrayal. La Diabla and Chalo plan to eliminate Gato Gordo and Titi in Mexico.
episodes.title: Corazón partido

episodes.synopsis: Virginia plays the role of Catalina Santana on her date with Titi. He is thrilled and invites her to Mexico. Martin organizes an operation.
episodes.title: El Titi, deslumbrado

episodes.synopsis: Virginia and Titi get to Chalo's ranch in Mexico but the TEA is on their tail. Las Diablas' hitmen kidnap Hilda at Marcial's burial.
episodes.title: Virginia se la juega

episodes.synopsis: Titi shoots Chalo and gunfire commences. Catalina la Grande joins in and Titi is surprised that she can use a gun. The TEA shows up at the ranch
episodes.title: El dominio de Virginia

episodes.synopsis: Virginia pretends to be sick and Titi goes out to get her medicine. She uses the opportunity to give Martín their location.
episodes.title: El Titi, a punto de caer

episodes.synopsis: Titi manages to flee the TEA. Virginia asks Martín to arrest her so that Titi isn't suspicious and he agrees so that she won't go back to Colombia.
episodes.title: Virginia bajo sospecha

episodes.synopsis: Martín secretly takes Virginia to a rented house. Aníbal get to Daniela's "aunt's" house. She seduces him and Yésica shows up to torture him.
episodes.title: ¿Una trampa de Martín?

episodes.synopsis: Virginia thinks that Martín is helping her but he has different intentions. Mariana manipulates Catalina la Pequeña.
episodes.title: Propósitos perversos

episodes.synopsis: Martín holds Virginia against her will and declares his love for her. La Diabla gets revenge and Titi looks for Chalo's competition.
episodes.title: Virginia en graves problemas

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla demands that Calvo seduce Hilda. Gato Gordo is at death's door but he has two last requests: one has to do with a crime.
episodes.title: Plan de seducción

episodes.synopsis: Catalina tries to trick Martín so that she can escape. The policeman is clever and she swears her revenge. Santiago finds Martín.
episodes.title: Intento de fuga

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro goes to Yésica's ranch to negotiate Hilda's freedom. Mayra pretends to be a narco by following La Diabla's instructions.
episodes.title: La maldad a flor de piel

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro insists on negotiating Hilda's freedom. Mariana goes to a drunk Nacho's house. She pretends to be Catalina la Pequeña to confuse him.
episodes.title: Misión imposible

episodes.synopsis: Mariana plays with Catalina la Pequeña's excitement. Catalina la Grande finds out that Hilda has been kidnapped. The past surprises Santiago.
episodes.title: La astucia de Mariana

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro sends a drone to find Hilda. Daniela and La Diabla go to Aníbal's funeral. Yésica speaks to the governor. Titi calls Martina about business.
episodes.title: La otra cara de Hilda

episodes.synopsis: Hilda hides from Calvo and La Diabla realizes that they're not there. Daniela glimpses a drone and warns her mother that she might be recognized.
episodes.title: Espías al acecho

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande tries to find Santiago and his kids but he makes an irreversible decision and leaves a letter. Nachito wants to rescue his love.
episodes.title: Una fría despedida

episodes.synopsis: Martina tries to kill Titi for all the humiliation he caused her. Catalina la Pequeña is suspicious of Mariana and talks to Hernán Darío.
episodes.title: El Titi las paga

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande and co. get ready to confront Las Diablas. Mariana and Sebastián leave because of their parents. Nacho tries to clear his name.
episodes.title: Madre angustiada

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande shows up heavily armed at Las Diablas' ranch and sparks a massacre. Hilda refuses to go with her family and everyone is shocked.
episodes.title: Rescate sangriento

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla takes Hilda to her new hiding place. A furious Catalina la Pequeña strangles Daniela. Catalina la Grande can't find her children.
episodes.title: Furia desatada

episodes.synopsis: Daniela escapes. Catalina la Grande is alone and suffering after her children and husband abandon her. Hilda considers teaming up with Yésica.
episodes.title: Terreno desconocido

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro and Yésica set up a meeting to exchange hostages. Catalina la Grande meets the new TEA boss. The new neighborhood pimp, Dayana, meets Titi.
episodes.title: La Diabla arma su ejercito

episodes.synopsis: Yésica coordinates the meeting with Albeiro for the exchange. The neighborhood pimp goes after Mariana and is surprised to see Catalina.
episodes.title: El juego de La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande and her boss set up a secure area for the exchange. Dayana is ready to start recruiting her next victim: Mariana.
episodes.title: Adolescente perdida

episodes.synopsis: Gunfire starts at the exchange and Albeiro and Jota are trapped. Dayana gives Mariana a hallucinogenic and she takes it, unaware of the consequences.
episodes.title: Una rebelde e ingenua

episodes.synopsis: Mariana is out of her mind due to the drugs and alcohol. She hallucinates that Titi is Hernán Darío and asks him to impregnate her.
episodes.title: Mariana entra en trance

episodes.synopsis: Mariana is repulsed after unabashedly sleeping with Titi. Yésica coerces Albeiro into her bed and takes photos to show Hilda.
episodes.title: La realidad de Mariana

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande tells Mariana that she can get marijuana under three conditions. Hilda sends Albeiro a video message.
episodes.title: La Diabla, en su gloria!

episodes.synopsis: Yésica fantasizes about having a family with Albeiro. Catalina la Grande is planning to track Daniela so she can find La Diabla.
episodes.title: La Diabla utiliza la magia negra

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Pequeña puts a tracker on Daniela and lets her go free. The TEA and the police take action. Gatillo betrays Las Diablas.
episodes.title: El rescate de Albeiro e Hilda

episodes.synopsis: Mariana is willing to go to extremes to get Hernán. At Titi's request, Dayana convinces Mariana to visit him again.
episodes.title: Maquinación

episodes.synopsis: Titi organizes Mariana's big birthday party. Catalina la Grande gives her daughter marijuana. Santiago tries to forget Catalina.
episodes.title: El Titi prepara un agasajo

episodes.synopsis: Las Diablas go to see the witch Abigail and Daniela asks her for some help. Catalina la Pequeña walks in on Hernán Darío and Dayana together.
episodes.title: Conjuros y rituales

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla freezes Albeiro's semen so she can have his child. Hilda calls Albeiro out for his infidelity. Las Diablas show up in the neighborhood.
episodes.title: El sufrimiento y la furia

episodes.synopsis: Yésica goes to an artificial insemination clinic. Hilda admits her feelings for Calvo to Albeiro. La Diabla hears from a secret admirer.
episodes.title: ¡El coraje de una madre!

episodes.synopsis: Las Diablas make it to Chalo's ranch and he decides to give Daniela the house. Catalina la Pequeña and Vanessa plan a trap. Dayana gets a beating.
episodes.title: La otra cara de Chalo

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande finds out that Chalo is still alive and that he and La Diabla want to kill her. Hilda says that she'll never get back with Albeiro.
episodes.title: Maleficio

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro is hurt by Hilda and turns to alcohol. Chalo has a proposition for Daniela. Everyone goes to Paola's daughter's funeral.
episodes.title: Morbosa obsesión

episodes.synopsis: Yésica gives Albeiro a concoction that the witch Abigail prepared. Mariana goes to the birthday party Titi is throwing and he gives her a fancy gift.
episodes.title: Hechizado

episodes.synopsis: Everything has a price for Las Diablas. The TEA deploys an operative to trap Yésica Beltrán. Daniel unleashes Daniela's fury.
episodes.title: Malas influencias

episodes.synopsis: Hours before the pageant, La Diabla tries to sway the judges' votes, unaware Catalina la Grande and her TEA partners are planning to capture her.
episodes.title: La corona tiene precio

episodes.synopsis: The beauty pageant winner is crowned. An order to kill is issued. The TEA finds out that Yésica is using her sister's identity.
episodes.title: Catalina gana el reinado

episodes.synopsis: A mother refuses to believe her daughter is dead and wants a different doctor to revive her. Mariana's daughter is born. Yésica receives a diagnosis.
episodes.title: La Diabla pierde a Daniela

episodes.synopsis: The TEA appoints Tony Campana as Catalina la Grande's bodyguard when they find out that Martín, the serial killer, has escaped from jail.
episodes.title: Asignan refuerzos a Catalina

episodes.synopsis: When she wakes up, Catalina la Grande sees a yellow rose with a note that Martín left her. La Diabla parades Daniela through the neighborhood.
episodes.title: Catalina vive su pesadilla

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande is willing to protect her daughter. Catalina la Mediana plans to kidnap Mariana's daughter to give her a DNA test.
episodes.title: La pesadilla de Catalina

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla tells a bewitched Albeiro that she froze his semen and hired a surrogate. The tension between Catalina la Grande and Albeiro explodes.
episodes.title: Albeiro quiere casarse

episodes.synopsis: The witch Abigaíl is targeted for failing to bring a dead person's spirit back to life. The spell on Albeiro is lifted.
episodes.title: Se rompe el hechizo de Albeiro

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro, conscious but tied up, convinces Yésica to let him go. Hilda shares secrets with Catalina la Grande. Yamilé escapes with La Diabla's son.
episodes.title: Le disparan a Albeiro

episodes.synopsis: Yamilé tells Catalina about the hell she endured while on La Diabla's ranch. Hilda finds out that Albeiro has a child with Yésica.
episodes.title: Catalina va por La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla stops El Cerdo from killing Albeiro and finds out that her child was kidnapped, so Calvo blackmails her. The authorities find a body.
episodes.title: Entre la espada y la pared

episodes.synopsis: Catalina plans to capture El Titi and La Diabla. Yésica orders Calvo to kill Yamilé and bring her the child that night.
episodes.title: El Titi compra un anillo

episodes.synopsis: Calvo sets out to prove his loyalty to La Diabla by following her orders. Catalina la Grande tells Hilda that Albeiro fell prey to black magic.
episodes.title: La Diabla se sale con la suya

episodes.synopsis: El Titi surrenders at Catalina's feet. La Diabla orders Calvo to kill Hilda. El Chalo finds out that Albeiro is at the ranch with Daniela.
episodes.title: El Titi complica a Catalina

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla returns to the ranch with an army to save Albeiro and her son from the hands of El Chalo and get back her daughter, who has been embalmed.
episodes.title: La Diabla mata a Chalo

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla orders photographic proof be taken of her latest feat, and makes a deal with Albeiro. Catalina la Grande tries to escape.
episodes.title: La Diabla tiene cómo negociar

episodes.synopsis: Catalina goes to live with El Titi to trap him. Catalina la Mediana gives her boyfriend's daughter a DNA test. La Diabla negotiates with the TEA.
episodes.title: Catalina y su misión peligrosa

episodes.synopsis: While Catalina la Grande distracts Cabras with an exotic dance, the TEA carries out the raid to find El Titi. Yésica is crazy about Albeiro.
episodes.title: Catalina se juega la vida

episodes.synopsis: In order to jumpstart her business again, La Diabla decides to stop the war with her enemy. Albeiro takes advantage of Yésica's absence to escape.
episodes.title: La Diabla contacta a El Titi

episodes.synopsis: El Titi professes his love for Catalina. Mariana is alone with the baby and Martín comes into the mansion. La Diabla organizes a meeting with Aurelio.
episodes.title: Catalina le da el sí a El Titi

episodes.synopsis: Catalina takes control in order to rescue Mariana and her granddaughter from Martín's grip. La Diabla is anxious when she doesn't hear from Albeiro.
episodes.title: Catalina salva a Mariana

episodes.synopsis: Catalina avoids a shoot-out with the TEA and escapes. She feels unsafe and flees with her family. La Diabla orders Calvo to kidnap Albeiro.
episodes.title: Catalina amenaza a El Titi

episodes.synopsis: La Diabla suffers a betrayal that gives Catalina la Grande a juicy opportunity. Hilda asks Albeiro if Yésica's child is his. El Titi flees.
episodes.title: Catalina caza a La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: Catalina helps the TEA to score a huge win, but a later accusation made against her changes her feelings toward the agency.
episodes.title: Catalina captura a La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: Desperate for information about El Chalo, the TEA enters into a negotiation with their prisoner, behind the Colombian government's back.
episodes.title: La Diabla nunca se rinde

episodes.synopsis: To finalize the deal with the TEA, the prisoner will need to be extradited to the U.S. Dayana wants Catalina la Mediana's head and seduces Villa.
episodes.title: Un ultimátum para La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: Lucía has hell in store for her after she is kidnapped. Albeiro reveals who the love of his life is. Yésica moves to a bunker.
episodes.title: Martín planea cocinar a Lucía

episodes.synopsis: Santiago receives joyous news. La Diabla meets Lucrecia. Lucía attempts to escape from her captor.
episodes.title: Catalina vuelve con Santiago

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro is confused about his feelings and can't manage to get Catalina out of his mind. He calls her but she is with Santiago.
episodes.title: Albeiro piensa en Catalina

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro admits that he has always been in love with Catalina but Hilda is his here and now. Zoraya escapes from the hospital and plots revenge.
episodes.title: Albeiro deja atrás a Catalina

episodes.synopsis: Catalina and Santiago tell Hernán Darío that they're going back to Miami and that they fear for their daughter's and granddaughter's lives.
episodes.title: Nachi no se alejará de su hija

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Mediana gives Nachito the DNA results. La Diabla refuses a proposal. The doctor tells Hilda her presence helps bring back Carlos's memory.
episodes.title: Nacho no es padre

episodes.synopsis: Mariana refuses to give her daughter another DNA test but Hernán Darío demands it. Hilda talks to Albeiro about Carlos and he agrees to help him.
episodes.title: Hernán Darío encara a Mariana

episodes.synopsis: Everyone believes the curse of the five women in the neighborhood has been lifted. Lucrecia gives La Diabla some advice. Nachito makes a promise.
episodes.title: Catalina sufre por Ximena

episodes.synopsis: Mexico's second biggest drug trafficker gives the order to kill Catalina's sister. El Titi warns her and she decides to go back to the TEA.
episodes.title: El Titi pasa el dato a Catalina

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande finds out who the father of her granddaughter is. La Diabla makes an outrageous demand.
episodes.title: Mariana se quita la máscara

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande is more determined than ever to capture El Titi. Mariana forms an alliance with Dayana.
episodes.title: El Titi en la mira de Catalina

episodes.synopsis: When she realizes that she won't be a good mother, Mariana decides to flee and live the life she's dreamed of. Strange things happen in the town.
episodes.title: Mariana renuncia a su hija

episodes.synopsis: Mariana tells the father of her baby about his child. The TEA changes tactics regarding the extradition of its prisoner.
episodes.title: El Titi se entera que es padre

episodes.synopsis: As revenge, Mariana plans to bomb Hernán Darío's house and blow up him and Catalina la Mediana together. La Diabla has a hidden enemy.
episodes.title: Mariana tiene aliados

episodes.synopsis: El Titi and Villa find out about the extradition to the United States and make a plan. Daniel wakes up in the hospital.
episodes.title: Emboscada contra La Diabla

episodes.synopsis: While the TEA relocates its prisoner, El Titi's thugs lie in wait to execute his plan. Jota repents. Miguel gives something to Yésica.
episodes.title: La Diabla camino a su fin

episodes.synopsis: The attack results in a bloody scene, with more than one casualty. Mariana finds out that her daughter is in Nachito's house.
episodes.title: La Diabla sobrevive el ataque

episodes.synopsis: Mariana and her baby's father race against the clock to rescue their daughter in time. Zoraya learns she saved the life of La Mano Negra.
episodes.title: Explota la casa de Nachito

episodes.synopsis: The doctors fight to save Hernán Darío's life. Unconscious, Nachito remembers what happened. Catalina la Grande is reunited with her father.
episodes.title: Nachito al borde de la muerte

episodes.synopsis: Upon hearing that only a miracle can save Hernán Darío, Catalina la Mediana accuses Mariana of being responsible.
episodes.title: Catalina acusa a Mariana

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande and the others don't know that Paola is under Laura's spell. La Mano Negra gives Zoraya and Mateo a new identity.
episodes.title: La maldición rodea a Catalina

episodes.synopsis: Hilda begins to doubt when she sees Albeiro and Catalina la Grande. Zoraya and Mateo leave their past behind. Mariana hatches a plan.
episodes.title: Albeiro en brazos de Catalina

episodes.synopsis: Albeiro confesses to Hilda that he will never forget Catalina la Grande. Catalina and Santiago lament upon learning their granddaughter was stolen.
episodes.title: Albeiro se sincera con Hilda

episodes.synopsis: El Titi is thrilled with his new role. Catalina la Grande hides information from the police. Hilda dresses Carlos in Albeiro's clothes.
episodes.title: El Titi no se separará de su hija

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande receives a big career opportunity. La Diabla already has her child in her hands. Zoraya learns part of La Mano Negra's plan.
episodes.title: Catalina recibe un ascenso

episodes.synopsis: Mariana risks revealing to Titi that her mother is a TEA agent, but he doesn't believe it. La Diabla has a blood sample from Albeiro.
episodes.title: Mariana traiciona a su madre

episodes.synopsis: Regretfully, Catalina la Grande confesses that she will pursue her own daughter like any other drug trafficker. La Diabla needs a face transplant.
episodes.title: Catalina se apega al deber

episodes.synopsis: Yésica Beltrán faces a harsh reality. A loved one is buried. El Titi is attracted to Mariana, who finds files that may help him.
episodes.title: La Diabla destapa su rostro

episodes.synopsis: Nachito believes that he does not have much time left and his last wish is to marry his love. La Diabla risks changing her face. Titi gets a DNA test.
episodes.title: Hernán Darío despierta

episodes.synopsis: The doctor agrees to operate on La Diabla, who asks for a new identity and donor. Catalina la Grande is appointed to her new position.
episodes.title: Donante de cara para Yésica

episodes.synopsis: Titi asks Mariana what she would like to study. She responds: the drug trafficking business. Catalina is sent to watch La Diabla's mother's house.
episodes.title: Mariana aspira ser como Yésica

episodes.synopsis: El Titi is surprised to hear that Mariana hates her mother and will stop at nothing to avenge her. Martín shows up at the clinic.
episodes.title: Mariana, la narco más joven

episodes.synopsis: Calvo helps La Diabla choose a new face for her transplant. Catalina and Nachito prepare their wedding. El Titi decides to put Mariana on the job.
episodes.title: Yésica elige su nuevo rostro

episodes.synopsis: After so many obstacles, Catalina la Mediana and Nachito get married in the hospital. Mariana tries to create her own cartel. Daniel meets Martín.
episodes.title: Catalina y Hernán Darío se casan

episodes.synopsis: While Nachito is suffering, Catalina la Mediana makes a discovery. La Diabla undergoes her transplant. Mendieta plots against Tony and Santiago.
episodes.title: Catalina está embarazada

episodes.synopsis: Following instructions, Santiago goes to the motel where he thinks Catalina la Grande and her escort are staying. Nachito gets a message from Marcial.
episodes.title: Santiago muerde el anzuelo

episodes.synopsis: Catalina la Grande loses trust in Santiago after seeing the mounting evidence. Daniel attempts to save Lucía. Jota falls into Laura's hands.
episodes.title: Catalina desconfía de Santiago

episodes.synopsis: Catalina has no idea that her biggest enemy is so close. La Diabla infiltrates the TEA with her new face and a different name.
episodes.title: La Diabla, escolta de Catalina
